188
00:21:08,058 --> 00:21:09,718
<font color="yellow">...atau apakah dia sehat-sehat saja...,</font>

189
00:21:10,958 --> 00:21:12,718
<font color="yellow">...atau apa dia dicintai...</font>

190
00:21:13,518 --> 00:21:15,488
<font color="yellow">Hal-hal seperti itulah.</font>

191
00:21:18,658 --> 00:21:21,688
<font color="yellow">Dia memang cantik, adikku itu.</font>

192
00:21:23,358 --> 00:21:25,788
<font color="yellow">Lanjutkan bicaramu.</font>

193
00:21:26,718 --> 00:21:27,758
<font color="yellow">Bicara tentang apa lagi?</font>

