00:21:28,288 --> 00:21:29,458
<font color="yellow">Hidupmu.</font>

195
00:21:29,818 --> 00:21:32,958
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana hidupmu dan bagaimana kau mati.</font>

196
00:21:34,288 --> 00:21:37,128
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah pernah cerita padamu.
